Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:21.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:26.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:31.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止める　その全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して　進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:46.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:51.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:56.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていれば　いつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:01.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえば　それは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％　自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:11.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％　誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:21.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分はダメだと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:26.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:21.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宽恕促人前行 仇恨让人停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:26.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:31.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅让你一直停滞不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:46.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名为永不凋谢之花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:51.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也无法永不凋谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:56.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}认真活着就会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:01.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此断言的话语必定是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之几十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:11.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之几不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:21.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:26.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原谅你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くこの手で掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして？　いま　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が解らなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境無く燃える焔　 群衆が指をさす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと強くなって　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したいひとを想い　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}闇をこの手で払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这样 追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要亲手去紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 则无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}强颜欢笑也一样 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法保护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？ 我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃尽万物的烈焰 饱受非议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保护所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心怀所爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}亲手驱散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}养父总是对哥哥特别对待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是对你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从小就严格地训练你 为了让你成为驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只是被培养成了保护哥哥的便利道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是自愿选择现在这条路的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟爸爸和哥哥无关
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都瞄不准了 内心还是很诚实的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么自己要被迫为了哥哥做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至今为止你已经想过很多遍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而哥哥本人却对你的辛苦毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已经受不了这种差别待遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厉害 好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你其实很讨厌哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.97,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,517)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(1074,605)}雪中松柏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不会上你的当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才想保持冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一直以来就是这样逃避自己的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:04.28,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么不能养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很憧憬哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明明救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但在憧憬的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是要酱油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 那是哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么时候布下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Corycia Melaina Cleodora Cleochareia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Bateia Drosera Solaia Periboea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}假装打偏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实际上是在用魔法弹画召唤水精的魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真的很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少要对自己坦诚一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我既喜欢又讨厌哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我更讨厌软弱无能的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真正讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}水精之水牢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稍微碰一下就会攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然看起来是建筑物 但果然还是魑魅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样下去就无处施加触地印 并以此为中心张开结界了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且也根本没时间去咏唱咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孢子囊附近有没有能落脚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我找找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孢子囊 好巨大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只听了一次结界咒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说实话 我没信心能完全记住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且就算张开了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要怎样才能打倒那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 那玩意好像巨大的肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没吃晚饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是的 居然还这么淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说实话 我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那还不是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}座位猜拳 石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你猜拳输了 这也没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是说这个 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是不能拔剑 你不就只是个拿着根棍子的怪力男吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就一点都不怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 下面有个岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有这里没有魑魅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 就在这里一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还没有自暴自弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说你才是 别怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在大家应该都在做自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们也来做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕小公主就专心布结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你说谁是小公主啊 信不信我戳死你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还不是因为你刚才一把鼻涕一把眼泪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不想当你这粗暴的公主的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 用不着你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要赢 胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们上 爱马小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才不是马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道他不仅仅只是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 叽尼叽尼 巴萨拉 巴叽尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管是老爸还是他 都一直在一个人硬撑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}简直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吽 怛罗吒 憾麦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕龙士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的结界咒 我确实听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火属性的结界？ 到底是谁做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这烟花真美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕你好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是帅呆了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好帅啊 胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姑且把结界布好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还是第一次召唤恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到会如此消耗体力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真能干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都没有手骑士称号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然能召唤这么多水精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但技术还不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是你的答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你比我想的更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就死在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把一个人类烧成灰需要多长时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我得看好时间才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥村 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像情况不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说不定马上就要破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难怪这附近的小喽啰速度变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打倒了还会不断出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}千万不要松开触地印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是松开了触地印 结界就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道 用不着你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我死也不会松手的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别一惊一乍的了 小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都说了别叫我小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是现在就紧张成这样 等下会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持好像成功张开结界了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们也要快点了 要赶在孢子囊破裂之前到达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要怎么快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}路都被孢子封死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造 这根锡杖给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩 快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}腐属性的东西怕火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要用这个逼退它们 慢慢前进的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先冷静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么点火只不过是个心理安慰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}单凭我们两个 冲上去和自杀没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持和大家肯定也会原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会有人责备我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家… 不只驱魔塾的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们的家人也在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真亏你能说出要自己逃跑这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是现在逃跑 我这一辈子都无颜面对明陀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连你都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都把恩情 责任 血脉 明陀什么的挂在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真是受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种东西不值得赌上生命来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种危急关头 你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死了就全完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志 志摩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是那种伟大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不来的话 我就一个人逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}薄情小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫 少住持 父亲 哥哥都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你最年长的矛哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是为了保护你和少住持而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的命是他救下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你今后可要好好活着 不能给他蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当我烦恼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就会问自己「如果是矛哥会怎么做」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矛哥是志摩家的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矛哥到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是我的锡杖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我承认你是志摩家的男人 所以把它托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要代表志摩家 好好保护少住持和子猫丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一切对我来说都太过沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么鬼明陀 血脉 恩情 全都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别缠着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 修呢嘛呢嘛嘛呢 嘛呢修修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果真的能抛弃这些 那该多轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}锡杖着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此 八百造大人召唤了乌枢沙摩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来咏唱真言强化你的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩你继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的假的 我一回来就让我冲锋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩对不起 我不该说你是薄情小人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孢子囊可能快要破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得快点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保 馔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真会使唤狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出来吧 保食兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出来吧 御馔津兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让它们抬着师父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然很小 但很有力气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上次野营的时候 化灯笼也是让它们搬运的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 我不能集中精神了 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说回来 我为什么在做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么那时候会想要帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己都搞不懂自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遇上他们以来 我的步调就乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之 约定好的事还是要办到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要活着回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同学 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什么都愿意做 你尽管开口就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特别是这家伙 看着就来气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不用勉强自己加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乖乖让人保护着不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保 馔 你们带着师父离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才不想被这种半桶水使唤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在做什么啊 我不能死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能抛下你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只会拖后腿 快逃啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小保 小馔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}师父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求求你 快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你现在不出来就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能一直这么弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须救神木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小 小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你愿意帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要先救神木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论孢子怎样腐蚀 我们都要种上加倍的绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好厉害啊 小尼 太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然能让绿男巨大化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你等着 神木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上吧 小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥 奥村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没完没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥村 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修呢嘛呢嘛嘛呢 嘛呢修修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}视野变蓝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的眼睛怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那一瞬间 我都本能地后退了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我觉得你很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但可能还是小看了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那不是你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是执着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真亏你能知道我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么大手大脚地放火 谁都知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你个老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你糟蹋了我所珍视的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要让你灰飞烟灭 给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:05.38,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第十集 不屈不挠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
